<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Book a Service - PetCare</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/assets/Favicon.ico" type="image/jpeg">
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/cb8535f973.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="header">
    <a href="/dashboard/user" class="logo"><i class="fa-solid fa-paw"></i>Pet<span>Care</span></a>
    <nav class="navbar">
      <a href="/dashboard/user">Dashboard</a>
        <a href="/user/services">Services</a>
      <a href="/user/bookings">Bookings</a>
      <a href="/user/pets">My Pets</a>
      <a href="/user/notifications">Notifications</a>
      <a href="/auth/logout">Logout</a>
    </nav>
    <i id="menu-btn" class="fas fa-bars"></i>
  </header>

  <section style="padding: 3rem 0; background: #f8f9fa; min-height: 80vh;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="
        color: var(--orange, #c88407);
        text-shadow: .4rem .4rem 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        letter-spacing: .1rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        text-align: center;
      ">Book a Service</h2>
      <form action="/user/book" method="POST" style="
        background: var(--white, #fff);
        border-radius: .7rem;
        box-shadow: .5rem .5rem 0 rgba(22, 160, 133, .12);
        border: .2rem solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem 2rem;
        max-width: 100%;
        margin: 0 auto;
      ">
        <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 1.2rem;">
          <label for="service" style="display: block; margin-bottom: .5rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--black, #1e1e1f);">Service</label>
          <select id="service" name="service" class="form-control" required style="width: 100%; padding: .8rem; border-radius: .5rem; border: .1rem solid var(--light-color, #ddd); font-size: 1rem;">
            <option value="">Select Service</option>
            <option value="Vet Visit" <%= service === 'vet' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Vet Visit</option>
            <option value="Grooming" <%= service === 'grooming' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Grooming</option>
            <option value="Training" <%= service === 'training' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Training</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 1.2rem;">
          <label for="date" style="display: block; margin-bottom: .5rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--black, #1e1e1f);">Date</label>
          <input type="date" id="booking_date" name="booking_date" class="form-control" required style="width: 100%; padding: .8rem; border-radius: .5rem; border: .1rem solid var(--light-color, #ddd); font-size: 1rem;">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 1.2rem;">
          <label for="notes" style="display: block; margin-bottom: .5rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--black, #1e1e1f);">Notes</label>
          <textarea id="notes" name="notes" class="form-control" style="width: 100%; padding: .8rem; border-radius: .5rem; border: .1rem solid var(--light-color, #ddd); font-size: 1rem;"></textarea>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <button type="submit" class="btn-submit" style="
            background: var(--green, #008000);
            color: var(--white, #fff);
            border: none;
            border-radius: .5rem;
            padding: .8rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
          "
          onmouseover="this.style.background='var(--orange, #c88407)'"
          onmouseout="this.style.background='var(--green, #008000)'"
          >Book Now</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="footer">
    <div class="footer-content">
      <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-paw"></i>Pet<span>Care</span></h3>
      <p>PetCare is a pet caring shop, where we provide facilities and various useful treatments. We offer Massage, a good ground, expert staff, good facilities and much more! Visit us anytime :). We are closed only on Thursday and our regular timings are 9:00AM to 10:00PM.</p>
      <ul class="socials">
        <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
        <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a></li>
        <li><a href="#"><i class="fa-brands fa-google-plus-g"></i></a></li>
        <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-youtube"></i></a></li>
        <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-linkedin-square"></i></a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="footer-bottom">
    <p>copyright &copy;<span id="currentYear"></span> <a href="#">Shode Miracle</a> - Pet Care All rights reserved.</p>
  </section>
  <script>
    document.getElementById('currentYear').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
